#                 the Moonlander, Voyager, and ErgoDox EZ; the
#                 same organization also maintains Oryx — the
#                 canonical web-based keyboard-layout editor —
#                 and Keymapp, the desktop companion app that
#                 kontroll speaks to over gRPC)
#   License    : MIT
